quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  2,113,"Yahuud en mbii nasaara en ngonaani e hay huunde nasaara en mbii yahuud en ngonaani e hay huunde, tawa e…ìe njannga deftere nde, ko noon …ìe nganndaa …ìe mbiinoo ko Alla √±aawata luural hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √±ande darnga"
  2,114,"Hombo …ìuri too√±e oon ka…óoowo yo innde Alla jante nder juulir…óe ombo daranii bonnude …óe …ìeen potaani naatde …óe so wonaa e kulol, …ìe ke…ìa koyeera e aduna …ìe ke…ìa lette maw…óe to laakara"
  2,115,"Fu…ónaange e hirnaange ko Alla woodani kala heen …óo kuccit, toon ko yeeso Alla, pellet Alla noon ko jaaj…óo e ganngal Makko piiltingal"
  2,116,"∆Åe mbii Alla Mo jogitii …ìi…ó…óo senaande woodanii Mo, nganndee kala ko woni e asamaanji e lesdi ko Kanko woodani fof na …óoftoo Mo"
  2,117,"Pu…ó…óu…óo asamaanji …ói e lesdi ndi, so O √±aawii huunde O wi'ata …óum tan ko: won …óum wona"
  2,118,"∆Åe nganndaa …ìe mbi'a mbela Alla haaldataa min wolla O addana min maande, ko noon adinoo…ìe ma…ì…ìe mbiinoo …ìer…óe mum en nanndi goonga tigi Min la…ì…ìinii maandeeji …ói wonande yim…ìe yananaa…ìe …ìe"
  2,119,"Minen Min nelirii ma goonga ngonaa beltinoowo jeertinoowo, A naa…ìntaake ma yim…ìe jayngol Jahannama"
  2,120,Yahuud e nasaara en mbeletaake ma haa njokkaa laawol ma…ì…ìe yo a wii …ìe nganndee ko peewal Alla woni peewal so a jokkii belee…óe ma…ì…ìe …ìaawo nde ke…ì…óaa ganndal ndeen a da√±ataa ballal Alla
  2,121,"∆Åeen …ìe Min ngaddani deftere nde e…ìe nde njannga no haaniri ko …ìeen tigi ngoon…óini nde, kala mbo yeddi nde ko …ìeen tigi ngoni bonnoraa…ìe"